# Vidkit
Video Player is made using HTML and javascript. 
It has all the basic functionality.
##Features

- [x] Adding toolbar.
- [x] Making toolbar functional.
- [ ] Adding playlist feature.
- [ ] Autoplay next song.
- [ ] Give previous and next button.
- [x] Play from the time last left.(Using localstorage)


##Usage

- Left Button to move 10 sec forward.
- Right Button to move 10 sec backward.
- Spacebar Button to pause/play the video.
- Up Button to Increase the volume.
- Down Button to Decrease the volume.
- Press 'M' to mute and unmute.


